Package: ConjugateDP
Type: Package
Title: The Stirling-gamma distribution: a conjugate prior for the Dirichlet
      process precision parameter
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alessandro Zito
Maintainer: The package maintainer <alessandro.zito@duke.edu>
Description: This package contains the random samples generator for the Stirling-gamma 
  distribution described in Zito, Rigon and Dunson (2023+). "Conjugate prior for the
  Dirichlet process precision via the Stirling-gamma distribution". 
